Models¶

LM¶

In [94]:
sample <- c_bank[c(1:100),]
usd <- sample$USD_840
eur <- sample$EUR_978
gold <- sample$gold

lm_gold <- lm(gold ~ usd + eur)

grid.lines = 50
usd.pred <- seq(min(usd), max(usd), length.out = grid.lines)
eur.pred <- seq(min(eur), max(eur), length.out = grid.lines)
xy <- expand.grid(x = usd.pred, y = eur.pred)
gold.pred <- matrix(predict(fit, newdata = xy), nrow = grid.lines, ncol = grid.lines)

fitpoints <- predict(lm_gold)

par(pin=c(6, 6))

scatter3D(usd, eur, gold, pch = 20, cex = 2, theta = 60, phi = 0,
    xlab = "usd", ylab = "eur", zlab = "gold",  
    surf = list(x = usd.pred, y = eur.pred, z = gold.pred, facets = NA, fit = fitpoints, col="grey"))
